summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of the alley in Block Seventeen (17), Boren Denny & Yesler'' Add. in the City of Seattle, by paving the same with brick to under Ordinance No. 24803, creating Local Improvement District No. 2378 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement
